      • partition

        public static rx.Observable<Options> partition(Options options,
                                               int horizontal,
                                               int vertical)
        Returns a sequence of Options that are same as the source apart from the Bounds which are partitioned according to horizontal and vertical parameters. For map-reduce purposes we need to be able to partition the bounds of Options. Passing horizontal=1 and vertical=1 will return one item only being a copy of the source Options.
        Parameters:
        options -
        horizontal - number of regions (with longitude)
        vertical - number of regions (with latitude)
        Returns:
